Source: odbc-fdw
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), unixodbc-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/devrimgunduz/odbc_fdw

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-odbc-fdw
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-odbc-fdw
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ODBC foreign data wrapper for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 odbc_fdw provides foreign tables backed by remote data sources reachable
 through unixODBC and an installed ODBC driver.
